  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate whether multiple nasal antigen challenges with dust mite allergen
      produces increases in nasal symptoms and local allergic inflammatory cells in the nose and
      the blood.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
